---
import Layout from '../../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import RelatedTools from '../../../components/RelatedTools.astro';

// Tool metadata
const name = "Calorie Burn Calculator";
const category = "health";
const tier = "Health & Fitness";
const description = "Calculate calories burned during exercise and physical activities based on standard MET values, weight, and duration.";

// SEO metadata
const seoTitle = "Calorie Burn Calculator | Walking, Running & Exercise";
const seoDescription = "Free calorie burn calculator to estimate calories burned walking, running, on a treadmill, doing yoga or any exercise. Get instant results by weight and time.";
const seoKeywords = "calorie burn calculator, resting calorie burn calculator, calorie burn calculator walking, daily calorie burn calculator, treadmill calorie burn calculator, walking calorie burn calculator, calorie burn calculator running, yoga calorie burn calculator, running calorie burn calculator, exercise calorie burn calculator, run calorie burn calculator, walk calorie burn calculator";
const canonicalUrl = "https://toolkify.com/tools/health/calorie-burn";
const ogImage = "https://toolkify.com/og-calorie-burn.png";
---

<Layout 
  title={seoTitle}
  description={seoDescription}
  keywords={seoKeywords}
  canonical={canonicalUrl}
  ogImage={ogImage}
  ogType="website"
  toolName={name}
  toolCategory={category}
  hideBanner={true}
>
  <!-- SEO JSON-LD Schema -->
  <script type="application/ld+json" is:inline>
    {
      "@context": "https://schema.org",
      "@type": "WebApplication",
      "name": "Calorie Burn Calculator",
      "url": "https://toolkify.com/tools/health/calorie-burn",
      "description": "Free calorie burn calculator that estimates calories burned walking, running, on a treadmill, doing yoga, lifting weights or any exercise. Personalize results by body weight, duration and intensity using standard MET (Metabolic Equivalent of Task) values.",
      "applicationCategory": "HealthApplication",
      "operatingSystem": "All",
      "browserRequirements": "Requires JavaScript. Requires HTML5.",
      "featureList": [
        "Walking calorie burn calculator",
        "Running calorie burn calculator",
        "Treadmill calorie burn calculator",
        "Yoga calorie burn calculator",
        "Daily and exercise calorie burn estimates",
        "Resting calorie (BMR) comparison"
      ],
      "offers": {
        "@type": "Offer",
        "price": "0.00",
        "priceCurrency": "USD"
      }
    }
  </script>

  <!-- FAQ JSON-LD Schema -->
  <script type="application/ld+json" is:inline>
    {
      "@context": "https://schema.org",
      "@type": "FAQPage",
      "mainEntity": [
        {
          "@type": "Question",
          "name": "How many steps to burn 1 calorie?",
          "acceptedAnswer": {
            "@type": "Answer",
            "text": "<p>On average, it takes about 20 steps to burn 1 calorie. The exact number of steps depends on your body weight, walking speed, and terrain. For instance, a person weighing 160 pounds (73 kg) walking at a moderate speed burns roughly 0.05 calories per step.</p>"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Question",
          "name": "What is my resting calorie burn?",
          "acceptedAnswer": {
            "@type": "Answer",
            "text": "<p>Your resting calorie burn, also known as your Basal Metabolic Rate (BMR), is the quantity of energy your body expends to support basic physiological processes (like breathing, circulation, cellular repair, and temperature regulation) at rest. For most healthy adults, this accounts for 1,200 to 2,000 calories per day, depending on biological sex, age, height, and weight.</p>"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Question",
          "name": "Does a calorie deficit burn fat?",
          "acceptedAnswer": {
            "@type": "Answer",
            "text": "<p>Yes, a calorie deficit is the fundamental physiological requirement for burning fat. When you consume fewer calories than your body uses, it extracts stored energy from body fat reserves, converting them into fuel and leading to fat loss.</p>"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Question",
          "name": "What is the average calorie burn per day?",
          "acceptedAnswer": {
            "@type": "Answer",
            "text": "<p>The average calorie burn per day varies depending on age, biological sex, muscle mass, and daily activity levels. In general, adult women burn approximately 1,600 to 2,200 calories per day, whereas adult men burn between 2,000 and 3,000 calories per day.</p>"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Question",
          "name": "How accurate are calorie burn calculators?",
          "acceptedAnswer": {
            "@type": "Answer",
            "text": "<p>Calorie burn calculators provide estimates based on peer-reviewed MET (Metabolic Equivalent of Task) values. While they are highly valuable benchmarks for workout and nutrition planning, they are not 100% precise as they do not capture individual biological variables like lean muscle-to-fat ratio, genetic differences, metabolic adaptation, or fitness level.</p>"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Question",
          "name": "How much calories do I burn calculator?",
          "acceptedAnswer": {
            "@type": "Answer",
            "text": "<p>To calculate how many calories you burn during exercise, input your body weight, duration of the activity, and choose the correct exercise from the list. The calculator will automatically apply standard MET values for the activity and compute your active energy expenditure.</p>"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Question",
          "name": "How to use a calorie burn calculator?",
          "acceptedAnswer": {
            "@type": "Answer",
            "text": "<p>To use a calorie burn calculator, simply enter your current body weight, the length of your workout session, and the specific physical activity you performed. The calculator will estimate the total calories burned using the standard physiological MET formula, helping you track your fitness targets.</p>"
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  </script>


  <section class="max-w-[1000px] w-full mx-auto px-4 py-3 sm:py-6 flex flex-col gap-3 sm:gap-4 animate-fade-in-up pb-16 print:p-0">
    <!-- Breadcrumb & Header -->
    <div class="flex flex-col gap-1 print:hidden">
      <nav class="flex items-center gap-1.5 text-[10px] font-semibold text-slate uppercase" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
        <a href="/" class="hover:text-primary transition-colors">Home</a>
        <span>/</span>
        <a href="/" class="hover:text-primary transition-colors">Tools</a>
        <span>/</span>
        <span class="text-brand-blue capitalize">{category}</span>
      </nav>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-center justify-between mt-0.5 gap-2">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 flex-wrap">
          <h1 class="font-display font-medium text-xl sm:text-2xl tracking-tight text-primary">
            {name}
          </h1>
          <span class="bg-surface-pricing-featured text-brand-blue text-[10px] py-0.5 px-2 rounded-full font-semibold uppercase whitespace-nowrap shrink-0">{tier}</span>
        </div>
        
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 flex-wrap">
          <button
            type="button"
            id="share-btn"
            class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 text-[11px] font-semibold px-2.5 py-1 bg-canvas hover:bg-surface border border-hairline text-slate hover:text-primary rounded-full transition-all cursor-pointer shadow-subtle"
            aria-label="Share tool link"
          >
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-3.5 h-3.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M8.684 10.742l5.028-2.513m0 7.544l-5.028-2.513M18 8a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm-6 8a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 0a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z" />
            </svg>
            <span>Share</span>
          </button>

          <button
            type="button"
            id="how-it-works-btn"
            class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 text-[11px] font-semibold px-2.5 py-1 bg-canvas hover:bg-surface border border-hairline text-slate hover:text-primary rounded-full transition-all cursor-pointer shadow-subtle"
            aria-label="How calorie burn calculator works"
          >
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-3.5 h-3.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13 16h-1v-4h-1m1-4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
            </svg>
            <span>How it works</span>
          </button>

          <button
            type="button"
            id="reset-btn"
            class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 text-[11px] font-semibold px-2.5 py-1 bg-canvas hover:bg-surface border border-hairline text-slate hover:text-brand-coral hover:border-brand-coral rounded-full transition-all cursor-pointer shadow-subtle"
            aria-label="Reset calculator inputs"
          >
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-3 h-3" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4 4v5h.582m15.356 2A8.001 8.001 0 1121.21 7.89M9 11l3-3 3 3m-3-3v12"></path>
            </svg>
            <span>Reset</span>
          </button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Workspace Container (Zero-Scroll Compact Layout) -->
    <div class="card-base p-4 sm:p-5 flex flex-col gap-4 print:border-none print:shadow-none print:bg-transparent print:p-0">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-5 items-stretch">
        
        <!-- Left Pane: Inputs -->
        <div class="flex flex-col justify-between gap-3 print:hidden">
          <div class="flex flex-col gap-3">
            
            <!-- Unit Toggle (Miro Pill Style) -->
            <div class="flex flex-col gap-1">
              <label class="text-[11px] font-semibold text-charcoal">Measurement Unit</label>
              <div class="flex rounded-full bg-surface p-0.5 border border-hairline self-start">
                <button
                  type="button"
                  id="unit-metric-btn"
                  class="text-[11px] px-4 py-1 rounded-full font-bold transition-all cursor-pointer text-slate"
                >
                  Metric (kg)
                </button>
                <button
                  type="button"
                  id="unit-imperial-btn"
                  class="text-[11px] px-4 py-1 rounded-full font-bold transition-all cursor-pointer bg-primary text-canvas"
                >
                  Imperial (lb)
                </button>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Weight Input -->
            <div class="flex flex-col gap-1.5">
              <label class="text-[11px] font-semibold text-charcoal flex justify-between">
                <span>Body Weight</span>
                <span id="weight-label" class="font-mono text-stone font-semibold">154 lb</span>
              </label>
              
              <!-- Metric Weight (KG) -->
              <div id="metric-weight-container" class="flex items-center gap-2 hidden">
                <input
                  type="range"
                  id="weight-metric-range"
                  min="30"
                  max="200"
                  value="70"
                  step="1"
                  class="w-full cursor-pointer accent-brand-blue"
                  aria-label="Weight in Kilograms Slider"
                />
                <div class="relative w-20 shrink-0">
                  <input
                    type="number"
                    id="weight-metric-input"
                    min="30"
                    max="200"
                    value="70"
                    class="text-input pr-7 py-1 text-xs text-center font-mono h-8"
                    inputmode="numeric"
                  />
                  <span class="absolute right-2 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 text-stone text-[10px]">kg</span>
                </div>
              </div>

              <!-- Imperial Weight (LBS) -->
              <div id="imperial-weight-container" class="flex items-center gap-2">
                <input
                  type="range"
                  id="weight-lbs-range"
                  min="60"
                  max="450"
                  value="154"
                  step="1"
                  class="w-full cursor-pointer accent-brand-blue"
                  aria-label="Weight in Pounds Slider"
                />
                <div class="relative w-20 shrink-0">
                  <input
                    type="number"
                    id="weight-lbs-input"
                    min="60"
                    max="450"
                    value="154"
                    class="text-input pr-7 py-1 text-xs text-center font-mono h-8"
                    inputmode="numeric"
                  />
                  <span class="absolute right-2 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 text-stone text-[10px]">lb</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Duration Input -->
            <div class="flex flex-col gap-1.5">
              <label class="text-[11px] font-semibold text-charcoal flex justify-between">
                <span>Duration</span>
                <span id="duration-label" class="font-mono text-stone font-semibold">30 mins</span>
              </label>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
                <input
                  type="range"
                  id="duration-range"
                  min="1"
                  max="300"
                  value="30"
                  step="1"
                  class="w-full cursor-pointer accent-brand-blue"
                  aria-label="Duration in Minutes Slider"
                />
                <div class="relative w-24 shrink-0">
                  <input
                    type="number"
                    id="duration-input"
                    min="1"
                    max="300"
                    value="30"
                    class="text-input pr-9 py-1 text-xs text-center font-mono h-8"
                    inputmode="numeric"
                  />
                  <span class="absolute right-2 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 text-stone text-[10px]">mins</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Searchable Activity Selection -->
            <div class="flex flex-col gap-1.5">
              <label class="text-[11px] font-semibold text-charcoal">Select Activity / Exercise</label>
              
              <!-- Search & Filter Controls -->
              <div class="flex gap-2">
                <input
                  type="text"
                  id="activity-search"
                  placeholder="🔍 Search walking, running, yoga..."
                  class="text-input text-xs h-8 flex-1"
                />
                <select
                  id="category-filter"
                  class="text-input py-1 text-xs h-8 w-[130px] sm:w-1/3 shrink-0 cursor-pointer border border-hairline-strong bg-canvas text-ellipsis overflow-hidden whitespace-nowrap"
                >
                  <option value="all">All Categories</option>
                  <option value="cardio">Cardio & Speed</option>
                  <option value="gym">Gym & Strength</option>
                  <option value="sports">Sports & Rec</option>
                  <option value="daily">Daily Chores</option>
                </select>
              </div>

              <!-- Scrollable Activity List -->
              <div 
                id="activity-list" 
                class="border border-hairline rounded-lg h-36 overflow-y-auto p-1 flex flex-col gap-1 bg-surface-soft no-scrollbar"
              >
                <!-- Items populated dynamically via Javascript -->
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Intensity Adjustments (Where relevant) -->
            <div id="intensity-container" class="flex flex-col gap-1 hidden">
              <label class="text-[11px] font-semibold text-charcoal">Exercise Intensity</label>
              <div class="flex rounded-full bg-surface p-0.5 border border-hairline w-full">
                <button
                  type="button"
                  id="intensity-light"
                  class="flex-1 text-[10px] py-1 px-1 rounded-full font-bold transition-all cursor-pointer text-slate text-center"
                >
                  Light
                </button>
                <button
                  type="button"
                  id="intensity-moderate"
                  class="flex-1 text-[10px] py-1 px-1 rounded-full font-bold transition-all cursor-pointer bg-primary text-canvas text-center"
                >
                  Moderate
                </button>
                <button
                  type="button"
                  id="intensity-vigorous"
                  class="flex-1 text-[10px] py-1 px-1 rounded-full font-bold transition-all cursor-pointer text-slate text-center"
                >
                  Vigorous
                </button>
              </div>
            </div>

          </div>

          <!-- Advanced Options Collapse -->
          <div class="border-t border-hairline-soft pt-2 mt-1">
            <button
              type="button"
              id="advanced-toggle-btn"
              class="w-full flex items-center justify-between text-[11px] font-bold text-slate hover:text-primary transition-all cursor-pointer py-1"
            >
              <span class="flex items-center gap-1">
                ⚙ Advanced Parameters (BMR Compare, Custom MET)
              </span>
              <svg
                id="advanced-chevron"
                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                class="w-3.5 h-3.5 text-stone transition-transform duration-300"
                fill="none"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                stroke="currentColor"
                stroke-width="2.5"
              >
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path>
              </svg>
            </button>

            <div id="advanced-panel" class="max-h-0 overflow-hidden transition-all duration-300 flex flex-col gap-3 mt-1.5">
              <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-3 pt-2 border-t border-hairline-soft/50">
                <!-- Biological Sex -->
                <div class="flex flex-col gap-1">
                  <label for="sex-select" class="text-[10px] font-semibold text-slate">Sex (for BMR context)</label>
                  <select
                    id="sex-select"
                    class="text-input py-1 text-xs h-8 cursor-pointer border border-hairline-strong bg-canvas"
                  >
                    <option value="male" selected>Male</option>
                    <option value="female">Female</option>
                    <option value="other">Other/Unspecified</option>
                  </select>
                </div>

                <!-- Age -->
                <div class="flex flex-col gap-1">
                  <label for="age-input" class="text-[10px] font-semibold text-slate">Age</label>
                  <div class="relative">
                    <input
                      type="number"
                      id="age-input"
                      min="10"
                      max="100"
                      value="30"
                      class="text-input py-1 text-xs font-mono h-8"
                      inputmode="numeric"
                    />
                    <span class="absolute right-2.5 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 text-stone text-[10px]">yrs</span>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-3">
                <!-- Custom MET Override -->
                <div class="flex flex-col gap-1">
                  <label for="custom-met-input" class="text-[10px] font-semibold text-slate">Custom MET Rate</label>
                  <input
                    type="number"
                    id="custom-met-input"
                    min="0.5"
                    max="25"
                    step="0.1"
                    placeholder="e.g. 5.5"
                    class="text-input py-1 text-xs font-mono h-8"
                    inputmode="decimal"
                  />
                </div>

                <!-- User Height -->
                <div class="flex flex-col gap-1">
                  <label for="height-input" class="text-[10px] font-semibold text-slate">Height (Optional)</label>
                  <div class="relative">
                    <input
                      type="number"
                      id="height-input"
                      min="80"
                      max="250"
                      value="175"
                      class="text-input py-1 text-xs font-mono h-8"
                      inputmode="numeric"
                    />
                    <span id="height-unit-lbl" class="absolute right-2.5 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 text-stone text-[10px]">cm</span>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="flex items-center justify-end mt-1">
                <button
                  type="button"
                  id="advanced-view-result-btn"
                  class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-[10px] font-semibold px-3 py-1 bg-primary hover:bg-charcoal text-canvas rounded-full transition-all cursor-pointer shadow-subtle animate-pulse"
                >
                  View Result &darr;
                </button>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

        </div>

        <!-- Right Pane: Results Dashboard Card -->
        <div id="results-card" class="card-feature-teal flex flex-col justify-between p-4 sm:p-5 relative overflow-hidden rounded-xl border border-moss-dark/10 print:border-none print:shadow-none print:p-0">
          <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-32 h-32 bg-teal-light/35 rounded-full blur-2xl pointer-events-none print:hidden"></div>
          
          <div class="flex flex-col gap-3.5 z-10 w-full">
            <!-- Card Header -->
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between border-b border-moss-dark/10 pb-2">
              <span class="text-[10px] uppercase font-extrabold text-moss-dark/70 tracking-widest">Active Calorie Estimator</span>
              <span class="flex h-2 w-2 relative print:hidden">
                <span id="status-pulse" class="animate-ping absolute inline-flex h-full w-full rounded-full bg-success-accent opacity-75"></span>
                <span id="status-dot" class="relative inline-flex rounded-full h-2 w-2 bg-success-accent"></span>
              </span>
            </div>

            <!-- Main Large Readout -->
            <div class="flex flex-col">
              <span class="text-[10px] uppercase font-bold text-slate block" id="exercise-name-lbl">Walking, moderate pace</span>
              <div class="flex items-baseline gap-1 mt-0.5">
                <span id="output-calories" class="font-display font-black text-3xl sm:text-4xl text-primary font-mono tracking-tight leading-none">123</span>
                <span class="text-xs font-semibold text-stone">kcal burned</span>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- MET details & weight context -->
            <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-3 border-t border-moss-dark/10 pt-3">
              <div class="flex flex-col">
                <span class="text-[9px] uppercase font-extrabold text-moss-dark/70">MET Intensity</span>
                <span id="output-met" class="font-display font-bold text-sm text-primary font-mono">3.5 METs</span>
                <span class="text-[8px] text-stone">Metabolic equivalents</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex flex-col">
                <span class="text-[9px] uppercase font-extrabold text-moss-dark/70">Relative Scale</span>
                <span id="output-ratio" class="font-display font-bold text-sm text-primary font-mono">3.5x rest</span>
                <span class="text-[8px] text-stone">Burn rate multiplier</span>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Equivalence reference comparisons -->
            <div class="flex flex-col gap-2 border-t border-moss-dark/10 pt-3">
              <span class="text-[9px] uppercase font-bold text-slate">Activity vs Food Equivalents</span>
              
              <div class="flex flex-col gap-1.5 text-[10px] font-medium">
                <!-- Banana -->
                <div class="flex flex-col gap-0.5">
                  <div class="flex justify-between text-slate font-bold">
                    <span>🍌 1 Banana (~100 kcal)</span>
                    <span id="eq-banana-pct" class="font-mono text-stone">100%</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="w-full h-2 bg-hairline rounded-full overflow-hidden">
                    <div id="eq-banana-bar" class="h-full bg-brand-yellow-deep" style="width: 0%;"></div>
                  </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Pizza Slice -->
                <div class="flex flex-col gap-0.5">
                  <div class="flex justify-between text-slate font-bold">
                    <span>🍕 1 Pizza Slice (~280 kcal)</span>
                    <span id="eq-pizza-pct" class="font-mono text-stone">45%</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="w-full h-2 bg-hairline rounded-full overflow-hidden">
                    <div id="eq-pizza-bar" class="h-full bg-brand-coral" style="width: 0%;"></div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Disclaimer alert text -->
            <div id="advice-box" class="text-[10px] text-moss-dark leading-relaxed pt-2 border-t border-moss-dark/5">
              <p>
                Calculations based on Metabolic Equivalents (METs). Individual rates vary based on muscle mass, body composition, fitness level, and actual effort.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>

      <!-- Action Button directly beneath input workspace -->
      <div class="flex justify-center pt-2 print:hidden">
        <button
          type="button"
          id="toggle-breakdown-btn"
          class="button-primary text-xs py-2 px-6 !rounded-full shadow-subtle hover:scale-105 active:scale-95 transition-all cursor-pointer flex items-center gap-1.5"
        >
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z"></path>
          </svg>
          <span>View Detailed Breakdown & Analysis</span>
        </button>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Detailed Breakdown & Analysis Section (Same Page) -->
    <div id="breakdown-section" class="max-h-0 overflow-hidden transition-all duration-500 flex flex-col gap-4 print:max-h-none print:overflow-visible">
      <div class="card-base p-4 sm:p-5 flex flex-col gap-4 mt-2 print:border-none print:shadow-none print:p-0">
        
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between border-b border-hairline pb-2">
          <h2 class="font-display font-semibold text-sm sm:text-base text-primary flex items-center gap-1.5">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-4 h-4 text-brand-blue" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5">
